messages.text: Liz! What r u up to? Want to come out tonight?
I’m gonna be at work late again
Omg your boss is such a witch
I have to send this contract off by midnight tonight though
Man, I knew your company had a tough rep, but I didn’t know it was that bad
Yeah…it looks like just me and my coffee mug here tonight…
isn’t this like the third time this week?
Yeah. And Jeff’s getting pretty sick of it
I feel so bad…he’s usually asleep by the time I get home
Not really what newly wed life is supposed to be like…
Can I do anything for u?
ya, u guys go have fun. I’ll catch up with u later
Keep me updated on how it’s going and we’ll hang this weekend
but did you just email me?
I got this weird email at the office just now
and it’s kinda freaking me out
I don’t know...that’s the weird part
it says it’s from an undisclosed address
he went out to a baseball game with his buddies
they said “someone who admires your work”
could it be someone from the office?
like a secret admirer or something? LOL
I can’t think of anyone who that would be
“better fill up your blue mug, looks like you’ll be there for a while”
how do they know your mug is blue?
I dunno…this is getting weird though
I could probably finish this up at home
k. I’ll text you when I get home
but all the doors are locked from the outside
I’m like seriously freaking out now
“where are you trying to go, Liz? Don’t you like it here?”
this sounds like a stalker or something
stay calm – everything’s gonna be ok
don’t text Jeff yet…I don’t want him to worry
can u hang on that long?
“why aren’t you at your desk working, Liz?”
what r u going to do???
I just went into the bathroom
and pushed up a chair against the door
the cops should be there any time now
I’ve never been so scared in my life
can u tell Jeff I love him plz?
just got another email on my phone
“I just wanted to make sure you were working hard”
it was Jordana, my psycho boss…
she was hiding in her office, like watching me
the police came and broke the doors open
she apparently had some sort of nervous breakdown when the company’s profits fell last quarter
her therapist told her she needed to take some time off work
can’t believe all this happened tonight!
at least I don’t have to finish that contract now ☺
